<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, October 7 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange on Wednesday stood at 1537.26 points, up
0.40 points compared to that on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
A total of 1,116,674 shares worth 3.78 billion rials (about
687,000 U.S. dollars) exchanged hands in 895 turns for 431
applicants. 
</P>
