is due here Wednesday night for talks with Egyptian President
Hosni Mubarak on the progress in the Palestinian-Israeli
negotiations, Egyptian Foreign Minister Amr Moussa said.
</P>
<P>
Moussa told reporters that Arafat will brief Mubarak on the
