<TEXT>
<P>
KAMPALA, October 7 (Xinhua) -- All three people on a Kenyan
registered plane escaped unhurt when it crash-landed at Patongo
in Uganda's northern district of Kitgum Wednesday afternoon.
</P>
<P>
The accident took place at 1:30 p.m., Radio Uganda reported
Wednesday evening.
</P>
<P>
