<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major World Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 8 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 11 major
world cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on October 9 issued by
China's Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 16 degrees C., max. 22 degrees C., clear to
overcast, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tokyo: min. 19 degrees C., max. 28 degrees C., cloudy to clear,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
