Prime Minister Blair also attended an international symposium
on the development of the capital market sponsored jointly by the
Shanghai Stock Exchange and the London Stock Exchange this
afternoon. He expressed his conviction that Britain's co-operation
with shanghai in this regard will further expand as this
symbolizes the bilateral friendship and cooperation between the
two countries.
</P>
