<HEADLINE> ASEAN Science, Technology Conference Opens in Hanoi </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANOI, October 8 (Xinhua) -- ASEAN's Committee for Science and
Technology (ASEAN COST) has opened a conference here in Hanoi to
promote cooperation among member countries in the fields of
science and technology, Vietnam News Agency (VNA) reported
Thursday.
</P>
<P>
The three-day conference, which opened on Wednesday, is part of
the fifth ASEAN Science and Technology Week, which runs October
5-15.
</P>
<P>
Participants are scheduled to discuss ASEAN development
strategies to strengthen cooperation and transfer in the fields of
science and technology, including the commercialization of science
and technology research, human resources development and the
future dissemination of science and technology information.
</P>
