Environment and ASEAN COST Vietnam representative Pham Khoi
Nnguyen opened the conference along with ASEAN COST President
Chong Lit Cheong.
</P>
<P>
The conference is a follow-up of the ASEAN unofficial summit
held last December in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia, at which
participants approved the ASEAN outlook for internal cooperation
and external relations through 2020. 
</P>
